{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Liquidiert.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't think they took it away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyhow, this stamp I remember-- liquidiert.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after a day or so, we were put in a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was still a normal train, but full of people, and crying, and with our possessions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember even SS man came, and somebody got a kind of flick, because he didn't stood up in the first minute.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was a normal train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was still a normal train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had still some food on the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we arrived to Theresienstadt, we arrived to a little village before Theresienstadt-- Bohusovice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then our luggage was taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, all the luggage was signed with the transport number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mine was BL214.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You will get it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some little carriers-- people took it away from us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had to walk quite-- I don't know-- let's say for a half and hour, maybe longer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we arrived in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we knew this building was called [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the place where they put us in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took and controlled all our possession-- I mean, the ones we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we really got the other parcels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got them back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And only some things they took out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a way of luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the moral is, we got them back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to a huge barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, we knew that it's the central barrack where all the high officers were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- at least my family-- came to a roof of this barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was in horrible condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The roof.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was overcrowded, filthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were sitting on the floor, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
